container_info.post_install_tip:
Please use the Menu > Fast Form On/Off 
to start to configure your Form.
You can Set Off/On  at specific Date and Time .
You can Stop Accepting Responses after a number of responses.

name: Fast Form On/Off
description: Fast Form On/Off is useful to limit responses and you can also schedule to Set On or Set Off a form to a specific Date and Time.
